---
---
<div class="contribute">
  <div class="contribute-glyph">+</div>
  <div class="contribute-body">
    <div class="contribute-title">Something missing?</div>
    <div class="contribute-copy">
      Every guide lives next to the code that implements it. Open a PR against
      <code>docs/guides/</code> — or file an RFC if you'd like the framework to grow.
    </div>
  </div>
  <a class="pr-btn ghost contribute-btn" href="https://github.com/mcp-rune/mcp-rune/discussions">
    Open RFC <span class="arr">→</span>
  </a>
  <a class="pr-btn acc contribute-btn" href="https://github.com/mcp-rune/mcp-rune/tree/main/docs/guides">
    Edit on GitHub <span class="arr">↗</span>
  </a>
</div>

<style>
  .contribute {
    margin-top: 24px;
    padding: 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124, 92, 255, 0.06) 0%, transparent 60%);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .contribute-glyph {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(124, 92, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 92, 255, 0.3);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--acc-2);
    font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .contribute-body { flex: 1; }
  .contribute-title {
    font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .contribute-copy {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--ink-3);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .contribute-copy code {
    font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
  }
  .contribute-btn { height: 38px; font-size: 13px; flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
